description: Beneficial Holdings, Inc., through its subsidiaries, operates in the real estate service sector in the United States. The company provides real estate development, asset management, and property and construction management services to owners of commercial real estate, corporations, institutions, and public sector entities. It is involved in the planning, financing, building, leasing, managing, acquiring, and selling a diverse set of projects, including residential, office, industrial, flex, retail, hospitality, and mixed-use properties. The company also offers solutions, such as evaluation, design, installation, finance, operations, monitoring, maintenance, and analytics. Beneficial Holdings, Inc. was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Montvale, New Jersey.
